Package FitnessClassManager

Class GymManager

java.lang.Object
FitnessClassManager.GymManager
public class GymManager extends Object
User Interface class that processes commands entered into the console Focuses on commands relating to gym member management, such as Add Member, Remove Member, Check In Member
Author:
Arya Shetty, John Greaney-Cheng

    • isValidMember

      private boolean isValidMember(String dob, String expire, String location)
      Checks if member meets all conditions to be added Conditions include: - Both birthday and expiration date of membership must be valid dates - Member's birthday can't be today or future date - Member must be over 18 - The gym location the member belongs to must exist
      Parameters:
      dob - birthday of the member
      expire - expiration date of the member's gym membership
      location - the gym the member belongs to
      Returns:
      true if member meets conditions to be added, false otherwise

      private boolean canCheckIn(String className, String fname, String lname, String dob)
      Checks if member meets all conditions to check in Conditions include: - Birthday must be a valid date - Member must exist in member database - Class to check into must exist - Member must have non-expired membership - Member must not have any time conflicts with other classes they're enrolled in
      Parameters:
      className - name of the class to check into
      fname - first name of the member to check in
      lname - last name of the member to check in
      dob - birthday of the member to check in
      Returns:
      true if member meets conditions to check into class false otherwise

    • isOverEighteen

      private boolean isOverEighteen(Date birthday, Date today)
      Checks if member is over 18 years old Compares birth year and current year to see if difference is greater than or less than 18. If difference is equal to 18, compares months and if months are equal, compares days.
      Parameters:
      birthday - birthday of the member
      today - current day's date
      Returns:
      true if member is 18 or older, false otherwise
